--- Added --- LagerhausRESTController for REST-Requests LagerhausDataService for Translation between DTOs, DataObjects and Resources LagerhausManager for Request to Database LagerhausBadRequestException for throwing in case of impossible conversion in LagerhausDataService

--- Added --- (initial version) DTO and Resource objects for external representation

--- Updated --- LagerhausManager -> for JPA usage pom.xml -> for JPA usage and for maven-builds
